kw.name: Open Browser
kw.doc: Opens a new browser instance to the optional ``url``.

kw.name: Set Selenium Speed
kw.doc: Sets the delay that is waited after each Selenium command.

kw.name: Start Video Recording
kw.doc: Starts the recording of a video in the background with the specified ``name``. The recording can be stopped by calling the `Stop Video Recording` keyword.

kw.name: Input Text
kw.doc: Types the given ``text`` into the text field identified by ``locator``.

kw.name: Input Password
kw.msg: Temporally setting log level to: NONE
kw.doc: Types the given password into the text field identified by ``locator``.

kw.name: Wait Until Element Is Visible
kw.doc: Waits until the element ``locator`` is visible.

kw.name: Element Text Should Be
kw.msg: Verifying element 'css:.alert.alert-danger.col-md-12' contains exact text 'Incorrect username/password.'.
kw.doc: Verifies that element ``locator`` contains exact the text ``expected``.

kw.name: Stop All Video Recordings
kw.doc: Stops all the video recordings and generates the files in WebM format. If ``embed`` argument was set to ``True`` the videos will be displayed in the log file.
